<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-65] Variables are not supported on status attribute a NullPointerException occurs if a variable is specified on the root log level.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-65</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following configuration causes a NullPointerException and the message &quot;null object returned for root&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;configuration status=&quot;${sys:log.level}&quot; strict=&quot;false&quot; name=&quot;DSI&quot; packages=&quot;com.terradue.dsione&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;appenders&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;Console name=&quot;Console&quot; target=&quot;SYSTEM_OUT&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;PatternLayout pattern=&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;%-5level&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; %msg%n&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/Console&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/appenders&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;  &amp;lt;loggers&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;root level=&quot;${sys:log.level}&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;appender-ref ref=&quot;Console&quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/root&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/loggers&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/configuration&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
